ough space (and even time) by harnessing electrogravitic effects as easily =
as a sailboat travels water propelled by wind. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(5=
4, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The bo=
ok is fascinating, and I recommend it, but if you just want to dip your toe=
